reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect toys for my 5 month old!
reviews.reviewText: I got these cars as a stocking stuffer for my five month old. He absolutely loves them! They have holes in the top for easy grabbing and the material is a soft silicone that is great for grabbing and putting in his mouth. The cars themselves are so cute and can move by themselves once pushed once. I love the details, like the cute turtle and the small hook on the tow truck. They also have a great rattle and jingle that keeps my son’s attention! I would definitely recommend them to anyone looking for something to keep your baby’s attention!
